  "body": "According to the [nodejs release schedule](https://github.com/nodejs/release#release-schedule), node 16 went into maintenance mode 2022-10-18.\r\nThe new active LTS is node 18.\r\n\r\nWe should upgrade all infrastructure, docs, guides, etc. to node 18.\r\n\r\nChecklist for completing upgrade:\r\n- [ ] CI/sim tests\r\n- [ ] Docker builds \r\n- [ ] Individual dev environments\r\n- [ ] Documentation upgrades\r\n- [ ] Upgrade test/production fleet of servers",
